c-5a11-47c1-8297-34af3c879e59","sourceId":"d4da6b5b-9916-46cd-ac80-3ae9bc780f71","charStart":4170,"sourceVersionId":"50e10024-f71d-4d49-ab5e-076e1e541a0c"},{"charEnd":1850,"chunkId":"cdfbfbef-a4af-4847-adc5-690b5e1c62c6","sourceId":"1602cb5c-021a-4f74-9abc-944fbb22c19e","charStart":850,"sourceVersionId":"d7444374-86d6-4ede-acf8-c1267f70328e"},{"charEnd":4298,"chunkId":"60bf048d-8963-452f-9312-f87ba87cec3a","sourceId":"1602cb5c-021a-4f74-9abc-944fbb22c19e","charStart":3298,"sourceVersionId":"d7444374-86d6-4ede-acf8-c1267f70328e"},{"charEnd":5969,"chunkId":"d022f79c-eff8-4412-ab33-3f46479b3888","sourceId":"1602cb5c-021a-4f74-9abc-944fbb22c19e","charStart":4998,"sourceVersionId":"d7444374-86d6-4ede-acf8-c1267f70328e"}],"metadataJson":{"response":{"answer":"The 2025 product roadmap for FieldCopilot is focused on expanding user base and enhancing customer satisfaction through various strategic initiatives. The overarching goal is to grow from 50,000 to 500,000 users while maintaining a customer satisfaction rate of over 95%. The roadmap is structured around key themes and priorities for each quarter. - In Q1 2025, the focus will be on polishing the product and improving performance, with a specific initiative to implement multi-tenancy for enterprise customers. [2]\n- In Q3 2025, the focus will be on integration with Microsoft 365 to improve search capabilities and unlock enterprise prospects. [2]\n\nWould you like me to go deeper on timeline, owners, or risks?","bullets":[{"claim":"In Q1 2025, the focus will be on polishing the product and improving performance, with a specific initiative to implement multi-tenancy for enterprise customers.","citations":[{"charEnd":5170,"chunkId":"c689b21c-5a11-47c1-8297-34af3c879e59","sourceId":"d4da6b5b-9916-46cd-ac80-3ae9bc780f71","charStart":4170,"sourceVersionId":"50e10024-f71d-4d49-ab5e-076e1e541a0c"}]},{"claim":"Q2 2025 will introduce real-time sync capabilities to enhance user experience by reducing latency.","citations":[{"char