o is responsible for fixing the AWS blocker and when is the deadline?","toolCallId":null,"citationsJson":null,"metadataJson":null,"createdAt":"2026-02-24T13:37:22.709Z"},{"id":"613f05cf-e433-46a4-bb00-fce67bd5ea5e","conversationId":"706ca2da-55d9-4479-8b95-eb8218d4a035","role":"assistant","content":"Jordan Martinez is responsible for resolving the AWS EU region quota blocker. - Jordan Martinez, the Infrastructure Lead, is managing the resolution of this blocker and is conducting daily check-ins with AWS. - The blocker poses a significant risk to the launch, impacting the ability to serve European customers and potentially affecting $500K in annual recurring revenue from key contracts. Would you like more information on the escalation process or the fallback plans in place?","toolCallId":null,"citationsJson":[],"metadataJson":{"response":{"answer":"Jordan Martinez is responsible for resolving the AWS EU region quota blocker. - Jordan Martinez, the Infrastructure Lead, is managing the resolution of this blocker and is conducting daily check-ins with AWS. - The blocker poses a significant risk to the launch, impacting the ability to serve European customers and potentially affecting $500K in annual recurring revenue from key contracts. Would you like more information on the escalation process or the fallback plans in place?","bullets":[],"sources":[{"id":"f7ada39b-e572-498c-8197-736a9a21f56f","url":"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pcwDpaqMVClET6mfadGy_oCYn4FgigJ-/view?usp=drivesdk","title":"JIRA_INFRA-1247_AWS_EU_Blocker.pdf","sourceId":"f7ada39b-e572-498c-8197-736a9a21f56f","sourceType":"drive","sourceTypeLabel":"Drive"}],"citations":[],"answer_text":"Jordan Martinez is responsible for resolving the AWS EU region quota blocker. - Jordan Martinez, the Infrastructure Lead, is managing the resolution of this blocker and is conducting daily check-ins with AWS. - The blocker poses a significant risk to the launch, impacting the ability to serve European customers and pote